; OMarkers (= SM/MM), DMarkers ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾\ {{{1

	; «↓» is position of indent 1
	; «x» is position of indent 2

	OMs:	OMs:
	as SM	as MM	DMarkers
	---		---		--------	; equiv Hy_Openers

	↓
	: x		:		::			;  (		) (
	L x		L		LL			;  [		] [
	C x		C					;  { 
	#: x	#:					; #( 
	#C x	#C					; #{ 

	↓
	': x	':					; '(
	'L x	'L					; '[
	'C x	'C					; '{
	'#: x	'#:					; '#(
	'#C x	'#C					; '#{

	~: x	~:					; ~(
	~L x	~L					; ~[
	~C x	~C					; ~{
	~#: x	~#:					; ~#(
	~#C x	~#C					; ~#{

	~@: x	~:					; ~(
	~@L x	~L					; ~[
	~@C x	~C					; ~{
	~@#: x	~#:					; ~#(
	~@#C x	~#C					; ~#{

	`: x	`:					; `(
	`L x	`L					; `[
	`C x	`C					; `{
	`#: x	`#:					; `#(
	`#C x	`#C					; `#{

